title: Cable 16 (2009) (Minutemen-Meganubis&DTs)
description:
Cable 16 (2009) (Minutemen-Meganubis&DTs)
Written by DUANE SWIERCZYNSKI
Penciled by PAUL GULACY
Cover by DAVE WILKINS

"WANDERLOST" We open literally one second after the shattering conclusion of "Messiah War," and Cable's mission to save mutantkind has never looked more bleak. In fact, you can't even call it a mission anymore... After all he's been through, after all he's survived...now all Cable can do now is pray-pray the heavily-armed killers roaming the deep future can't match his survival skills. And what is the fate of Hope-the so-called "Mutant Messiah"?
